update script stashes, pulls, and then applies user changes

Sway:

input type:touchpad {
	natural_scroll enabled
	tap enabled
	dwt enabled
}

input * xkb_layout "gb"


High DPI support:
https://ask.fedoraproject.org/t/hwo-to-increase-the-size-of-tty-font/2604/2

/etc/vconsole.conf
KEYMAP="gb"
FONT="latarcyrheb-sun32.psfu.gz"
